@page "/about"

<PageTitle>About - My Mountain Adventures</PageTitle>

<div class="about-container">
    <div class="about-content">
        <h1>About This Site</h1>
        <p>Welcome to My Mountain Adventures! This is a personal collection of videos from my hiking and mountain exploration journeys.</p>

        <h2>Features</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>🎥 High-quality video gallery</li>
            <li>📍 Location information for each adventure</li>
            <li>🔐 Secure content management</li>
            <li>💫 Beautiful, responsive design</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Technology</h2>
        <p>Built with modern web technologies:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>ASP.NET Core 8.0 with Blazor Server</li>
            <li>Entity Framework Core for data management</li>
            <li>SQL Server for reliable storage</li>
            <li>Responsive design with CSS animations</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
.about-container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 60px auto;
    padding: 40px;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
}

.about-content h1 {
    color: #2c3e50;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.about-content h2 {
    color: #667eea;
    margin-top: 30px;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
}

.about-content p {
    color: #7f8c8d;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    line-height: 1.8;
}

.about-content ul {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 15px 0;
}

.about-content li {
    padding: 10px 0 10px 30px;
    position: relative;
    color: #7f8c8d;
}

.about-content li:before {
    content: "→";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #667eea;
    font-weight: bold;
}
</style>
